cells.data: -- unzip4 :: [(a,b,c,d)] -> ([a],[b],[c],[d])on unzip4(wxyzs)	set ws to {}	set xs to {}	set ys to {}	set zs to {}	repeat with wxyz in wxyzs		set end of ws to |1| of wxyz		set end of xs to |2| of wxyz		set end of ys to |3| of wxyz		set end of zs to |4| of wxyz	end repeat	return Tuple4(ws, xs, ys, zs)end unzip4
